{"tid":1630551,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"整個網絡包括重鐵(機場快綫除外)及輕鐵的服務暫停","createTime":"2019-10-06T12:52:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T13:49:42.000Z","uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4ea41e095320db009d2e4b70abf73823a317ba47","tid":1630551,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:52:23.000Z","msg":"由於港鐵網絡內有大量車站因被嚴重破壞而關閉，未能為乘客提供安全及正常的服務，港鐵決定暫停整個網絡包括重鐵(機場快綫除外)及輕鐵的服務。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />幾時收皮????"},{"pid":"5b12114d0214762069ac858ba13e7f369c9bd4ff","tid":1630551,"uid":287032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:49:42.000Z","msg":"黨鐵<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">春袋</span></span>係<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">控制室</span></span><br />\n好多車站開唔到都係因為控制室維修唔到<br />\n因為所有訊號同指示都係由控制室傳達"}]}